      "summary": "310P 量化方案子包的入口文件，通过导入四个具体的 W8A8 方法模块来触发各方案在本地注册表中的注册。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "barrel", "quantization", "registry"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "Python 包 __init__.py 作为 barrel，通过 import 副作用触发装饰器注册，自身不导出符号。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:_310p/quantization/methods/registry.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "registry.py",
      "filePath": "_310p/quantization/methods/registry.py",
      "summary": "提供 310P 量化方案的本地注册表，以 (quant_type, layer_type) 为键映射到方案类，并暴露注册装饰器与查询函数。",
      "tags": ["registry", "quantization", "factory", "utility"],
      "complexity": "simple",
      "languageNotes": "使用模块级 dict 作为注册表，配合装饰器工厂实现按 (量化类型, 层类型) 的方案分发。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:_310p/quantization/methods/w8a8_base.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "w8a8_base.py",
      "filePath": "_310p/quantization/methods/w8a8_base.py",
      "summary": "定义 310P W8A8 线性层量化方案的基类，提供权重与 per-tensor / per-channel 量化参数的张量创建接口供子类复用。",
      "tags": ["quantization", "data-model", "base-class", "w8a8"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:_310p/quantization/methods/w8a8_dynamic.py",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "w8a8_dynamic.py",
      "filePath": "_310p/quantization/methods/w8a8_dynamic.py",
      "summary": "实现 310P W8A8 动态量化方法，覆盖 FusedMoE 与 Linear 两种层类型，包含权重创建、动态 per-token 量化以及 NPU quant matmul 推理逻辑。",
      "tags": ["quantization", "w8a8", "moe", "service", "npu"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "通过 torch_npu.npu_dynamic_quant 做激活动态量化、npu_quant_matmul 执行量化矩阵乘，并在加载后 process_weights_after_loading 中做 NZ 转换与权重布局调整。"
    },
    {
