      "summary": "实现 310P W8A8 静态量化的 Linear 方法，使用预置 scale/offset 完成激活量化与 NPU quant matmul，并在加载后调整权重布局。",
      "tags": ["quantization", "w8a8", "service", "npu", "static"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
